Package: CANOPE
Type: Package
Title: Copy-number Analysis using Normalized Observation Profiling for Exomes
Version: 0.1.0
Author: TL
Maintainer: TL <lavauxt@gmail.com>
Description: An R package for detecting copy number variations (CNVs) in targeted and exome sequencing data using low-variance reference sample selection and hidden Markov modeling.
